    <p class="sl-hero-sub">
      Discover the healing power of art therapy. 75 effective techniques to manage anxiety, depression, and PTSD through creative activities that help you understand yourself and process difficult thoughts.
    </p>
    <div class="sl-hero-actions">
      <form action="/cart/add" method="post" style="margin:0;">
        <input type="hidden" name="id" value="{{ book_variant.id }}">
