        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
    <div class="sl-hero-img">
      {%- if book_product.images.first -%}
        <img src="{{ book_product.images.first | img_url: 'master' }}" alt="{{ book_product.title }}" loading="eager" />
      {%- else -%}
        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg,#f3ebf6,#e9d8fd); width:100%; max-width:520px; margin:0 auto; height:380px; border-radius:20px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:#6b46c1; font-weight:800; font-size:1.1rem; border: 1px solid #d6bcfa;">
          🎨 Essential Art Therapy Exercises
        </div>
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- TRUST BAR -->
  <div class="sl-trust">
    <div class="sl-trust-item"><span>🎨</span> 75 Creative Exercises</div>
    <div class="sl-trust-item"><span>🖌️</span> No Experience Needed</div>
    <div class="sl-trust-item"><span>🧠</span> CBT-Based Healing</div>
    <div class="sl-trust-item"><span>⚡</span> Instant Access</div>
  </div>

  <!-- ABOUT THE BOOK -->
  <div class="sl-section" style="background: var(--surface);">
    <div class="sl-section-inner">
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <div class="sl-label">About the Book</div>
        <h2 class="sl-title">Gain Self-Awareness & Process Emotions</h2>
        <p class="sl-hero-sub" style="margin: 0 auto; max-width: 740px;">
          The purposeful act of making art can be more than a creative outlet. It can also help individuals gain self-awareness, process difficult thoughts, and even ease the effects of past traumas. Essential Art Therapy Exercises offers a range of creative activities to help you develop control over your emotions and aid the healing process.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="sl-grid-3">
        <div class="sl-card">
          <div class="sl-card-body">
            <div class="sl-card-icon">🎨</div>
            <div class="sl-card-title">Healing & Discovery</div>
            <div class="sl-card-text">75 strategic art therapy activities offer new opportunities for self-expression and tools for coping with mood and personality disorders.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sl-card">
          <div class="sl-card-body">
            <div class="sl-card-icon">💡</div>
            <div class="sl-card-title">Supportive Prompts</div>
            <div class="sl-card-text">Each exercise includes an explanation of its purpose and potential outcomes along with a series of insightful post-activity questions.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sl-card">
          <div class="sl-card-body">
            <div class="sl-card-icon">🖌️</div>
            <div class="sl-card-title">Judgment-Free Guidance</div>
            <div class="sl-card-text">Learn the basics of different artistic techniques and mediums, like drawing, painting, and sculpting―no previous art experience necessary.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- QUOTE -->
  <div class="sl-section">
    <div class="sl-section-inner">
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-light), #fff); border: 1px solid #d6bcfa; border-radius: 24px; padding: 48px; text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(107,70,193,0.05);">
        <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--brand-dark); line-height: 1.5; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 24px;">
          “This is a very worthwhile book for art therapists and for people who simply want to get creative and relax. Everything is explained clearly, understandably, and concisely.”
        </p>
